Grants {g|Encyclopedia:MomentumWithDetailsGlossary}momentum{/g} equal to {uip|Momentum|85e6ce25a6d64313b9ff39a8013d1b43}.
This {g|Encyclopedia:Ability}ability{/g} also grants an additional {unit_stat|WarhammerWillpower|bonus} momentum for each enemy that is either in a 5-cell radius around the Sister of Battle or was {g|Encyclopedia:HitSequenceGlossary}hit{/g} by her this {g|Encyclopedia:Turn}turn{/g}. If the Sister of Battle hits a daemon or Chaos cultist, the additional amount of momentum doubles.{br}
! Can only be used once per combat.

Proporciona {g|Encyclopedia:MomentumWithDetailsGlossary}ímpetu{/g} igual a {uip|Momentum|85e6ce25a6d64313b9ff39a8013d1b43}.
Esta {g|Encyclopedia:Ability}capacidad{/g} también proporciona {unit_stat|WarhammerWillpower|bonus} de ímpetu adicional por cada enemigo que esté en un radio de 5 casillas de la Hermana de Batalla o que haya sufrido un {g|Encyclopedia:HitSequenceGlossary}impacto{/g} de sus ataques este {g|Encyclopedia:Turn}turno{/g}. Si la Hermana de Batalla golpea a un daemon o a un cultista del Caos, el ímpetu adicional se duplica.{br}
! Solo puede usarse una vez por combate.

{uip|Momentum|85e6ce25a6d64313b9ff39a8013d1b43}に等しい{g|Encyclopedia:MomentumWithDetailsGlossary}推進力{/g}を与える。
さらにこの{g|Encyclopedia:Ability}アビリティ{/g}は、バトルシスターの周囲5マス以内にいる敵、またはこの{g|Encyclopedia:Turn}ターン{/g}でバトルシスターの{g|Encyclopedia:HitSequenceGlossary}攻撃を受けた{/g}敵の数だけ追加で{unit_stat|WarhammerWillpower|bonus}の推進力を与える。バトルシスターがディーモンかケイオス・カルティストに攻撃を当てた場合、追加される推進力は2倍になる。{br}
! 1回の戦闘につき1度だけ使用可能。

{uip|Momentum|85e6ce25a6d64313b9ff39a8013d1b43} kadar {g|Encyclopedia:MomentumWithDetailsGlossary}momentum{/g} kazandırır.
Ayrıca {g|Encyclopedia:Ability}kabiliyet{/g}, Harp Rahibesi'ne en fazla 5 hücre mesafede duran veya o {g|Encyclopedia:Turn}turda{/g} Harp Rahibesi tarafından {g|Encyclopedia:HitSequenceGlossary}vurulan{/g} her düşman için {unit_stat|WarhammerWillpower|bonus} puanlık ilave momentum kazandırır. Harp Rahibesi bir iblise veya Kaos tarikatçısına vurursa ilave momentum miktarı iki katına çıkar.{br}
! Her çatışmada sadece bir kez kullanılabilir.
